Job presets
Opinionated one-call job builders for common CI patterns. Each returns WorkflowBuilder so they chain:
wfb = Workflow('ci')
wfb.on.push(branches=['main'])
doc = wfb.uv_test_job().uv_lint_job().uv_pypi_job().build()

