WorkflowBuilder.docker_job

def docker_job(
    app_name:str, needs:str='test'
)-&gt;WorkflowBuilder:

Add a Docker build+push job targeting GHCR with a simple latest tag.
This is a quick preset for GHCR deploys. For production workflows with semver/sha tags use [docker_build_push()](https://vedicreader.github.io/gheasy/workflow.html#docker_build_push) which employs metadata-action.

